<h2 class="bold font-l">Ovens are Always Safe</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Owen read online that he can get his oven hot enough for his pizza by leaving the oven on broil so it can heat up overtime and they wouldn't put that information online if it wasn't safe. </p>
</div>
</div>
